LORD ELDER came back on the line, "I am not sure if Tuscon can hear me
yet. The energy field is fading." There was a hint of hope in his
voice as he spoke.

Meanwhile around PERCEPTOR, WINDLORD and NIGHTSHIFT the tunnel has
gone completely dark and silent. Except for what sounds and movements
they themselves were making, there was no other sound or movement that
could be discerned.

That is until far behind WINDLORD and PERCEPTOR there were sound the
sound of rumbling. Could someone be trying to block the doorway they
had come in through?

(TAG)

- Preston
